 />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a04cbfb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"b53a6f4ca8510ac1846ab7de414ff76f7ae8a6d4","tid":1728224,"uid":46535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VGBO4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VGBO4H.jpg&h=07add7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpayRh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpayRh4.jpg&h=c0c9cd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n箭咀位未知係未死去的頭髮，定生長出黎的頭髮"},{"pid":"db21386699266fba51df943568d05cb03af54870","tid":1728224,"uid":277652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53a6f4ca8510ac1846ab7de414ff76f7ae8a6d4","tid":1728224,"uid":46535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VGBO4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VGBO4H.jpg&h=07add7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpayRh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpayRh4.jpg&h=c0c9cd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n箭咀位未知係未死去的頭髮，定生長出黎的頭髮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:43:26.000Z","msg":"你D頭髮仲咁濃密, 唔好玩啦。"},{"pid":"f4eb07d67bdc0957abcb969c0c900a288c3858b7","tid":1728224,"uid":46535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAGVTto.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAGVTto.jpg&h=036d34b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22/11"},{"pid":"9de